{"tid":1853852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國家衛健委：已治癒患者仍有可能再次感染","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:45:49.000Z","uid":41404,"like":252,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e1075bd1e9350acc801e5bef8c3355bb815748","tid":1853852,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"據人民日報消息 1月31日15時，國家衛健委召開新聞發佈會，介紹當前疫情防控工作中重點人群和社區組織的健康防護情況。<br />\n<br />\n發佈會上，有關負責人表示，從一般的病毒感染規律來看，病毒感染之後都會產生一定的抗體，對人體產生保護作用。但是有的抗體可能持續時間沒有那麼長，所以這些已經痊癒的患者還是有再感染的風險，因此治癒的患者應該加強防護。"},{"pid":"ae29a8a5fc69e12bf839e8c07d8f229fa0d8e3b7","tid":1853852,"uid":155818,"like":105,"dislike":2,"score":103,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"退燒當醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a837dad38b9fa638406af492fdefed150be91bca","tid":1853852,"uid":136457,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回力鏢"},{"pid":"417306a9334564814283a8c9feff9575d4975430","tid":1853852,"uid":77196,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"諗起某個POST叫巴打中咗招先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9950ac0f9f436cef4ccf08d62bd64aa7451453d7","tid":1853852,"uid":321618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"未治癒啫 沒事兒<br />\n<br />\n 借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n一齊收港共支共皮<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht