<br />\n南边围村是多姓氏族群，所以强壮的原因并非血统，而是另一样东西！猜到了吗？就是这样，水源！南边围村水源比香港其他地区独特，水内含有多种对生物有益的抗原，植物吸收来自土壤中的水分，当区植物的生命力也特别强。而植物每朝的露水，经过挥发，水份带同植物养分回归大气，当地居民吸入了这些空气，身体自然便强壮起来！<br />\n<br />\n各位读者，不妨去亲身体验村内清新无比的空气，即使脱下口罩，也不怕被病毒入侵感染，此乃真实的体验！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#认同请转发，分享是美德，好人一生平安。"},{"pid":"f7559a882965f069d50263a0c903e90a48b873f9","tid":1853852,"uid":233429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:08:06.000Z","msg":"有可能=已經出現"},{"pid":"02790b9255fe75cb9c0ea9239c571d2acd214b7d","tid":1853852,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"病完又病... 病完又病..."},{"pid":"2a5394424eb1182d7e37c40af26af5ad350fa437","tid":1853852,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"中國從此萬劫不復"},{"pid":"ef97a1a060a52af8b08f7da890c6c588906ecb7a","tid":1853852,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d770bc8d744e594100bf4c891ba9c6ceea0caad4","tid":1853852,"uid":276548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"支那已治癒定義係咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"有心跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc62410f0e09b33606bd4316ad86975921f1d4e4","tid":1853852,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04b6b6bcfcb0892c786a804c0f5b80a251f95d8f","tid":1853852,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"係咪唔止一隻病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係, 點解LEAK 淨係LEAK 到一隻"},{"pid":"5036886929cdd5e8de0e24fb7cea38c6d1a1091d","tid":1853852,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"真係好翻就有抗體啦"},{"pid":"3bac1c1a6499289a51e7c2cbd1d6830e4fa1af91","tid":1853852,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:10:17.000Z","